{"tid":541727,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"獨媒報導既浸大豁免試內容同官方及學生會反映既不符？","createTime":"2018-01-26T17:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T18:07:39.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2c81077369fd2611447ea3f4efece4fb85a71cec","tid":541727,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T17:46:01.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯題目與普通話無關 難以捉摸評分標準<br />\n<br />\n談到豁免試內容，林同學指考試時間不長，只有約15至20分鐘。她認同考試頗難<span style=\"color: red;\">，<strong>第一部分先要分辨普通話和廣東話的詞語，然後第二部分為口試，討論一條類似通識題的辯題。她面對的兩題為「共享單車在香港可否成功」及「如何在香港興建更多中醫院」。她認為「根本唔係日常溝通用的普通話」，</span></strong>指同學若對有關議題並不認識的話，即使以廣東話亦難以討論，何況是以普通話進行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1054793\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1054793&d=NCCFNTZPnm%2BU3LfcVyTg%2FWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=e0625131\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1054793&h=5ad9f76e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1054793</a><br />\n<br />\n應該係三部分而唔係兩部分，冇左第三部分cosplay *7嗰段<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/014524_3d190d479dc9a643944527d406e125c3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F014524_3d190d479dc9a643944527d406e125c3.png&h=c51176fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/014527_a05b9e985e9a07efe53e796632bbc962.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F014527_a05b9e985e9a07efe53e796632bbc962.png&h=a9ee7804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lc.hkbu.edu.hk/det/doc/det-sample.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flc.hkbu.edu.hk%2Fdet%2Fdoc%2Fdet-sample.pdf&d=NCCFNTZPnm%2BU3LfcVyTg%2FWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=31160dbe\" target=\"_blank\">http://lc.hkbu.edu.hk/det/doc/det-sample.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e56691b5e3731695d54ce0621dc79a79236d045","tid":541727,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T18:07:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老味我明啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">獨媒係將有課程讀既普通話水平測試既考試內容，當撚左係豁免試黎講!!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n'普通話水平測試的命題說話只有一題，佔總分30%，且會給兩題任選其一。總共有30則說話題目作為考綱範圍，每次考試都是從這30題中抽出兩題供考生自選。30個題目皆為開放式，語句簡短，只是對話題範圍的規定，並不規定話題具體內容，因而考生無需代入情景角色，發揮空間也遠大過豁免試。'"},{"pid":"88404ab8ad442063fe50e9727e50cafa5c63a4ed","tid":541727,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T18:07:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老味報假新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}